This name has not been in use for many years, and has been variously associated with 
<taxonomicName authority="Vahl" authorityName="Vahl" authorityYear="1804" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" genus="Salvia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="lavandulifolia">
